,"msg":"pc 可以用4k 解像度<br />\n但 switch 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1080P都唔足(960p) 仲要 30fps"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"隻game 都無4K,材質又無4K<br />\n你用模擬器係出唔到4K野,你只係出到像素倍大左4畫面<br />\n唔通你玩GBA模擬器又叫玩4K咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nFurther testing may prove otherwise, but right now our contention is that The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild switches between two resolutions depending on configuration - so to confirm, that's 648p/720p on Wii U and Switch mobile, and 810p/900p on the docked Switch. <br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwii U  得720P,switch dock mode 900p<br />\n<br />\n720P 仲要倍上去4K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"2D同3D唔同<br />\n所有3D Model都係單純點同點連線、貼圖<br />\n無錯Texture係無4K, 但3D可以由Render 720p畫面變成Render做4K畫面<br />\n畫面一樣會清咗, 而且有Cemu有MOD可以改Level of Detail、View Distance<br />\n真係可以靚過Console玩<br />\n不過就真係少數PC先頂得順"},{"pid":"6a99004664d142333d04ab8a7939c8f4ba4607e9","tid":717042,"uid":35393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb44d8a29c5101269a77a6534c55bae2f5c599f4","tid":717042,"uid":44718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6f8d65b972c1f00ce526e0d75c49ef467ae4155b","tid":717042,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96445680d75b0085f9936321485fcae3cc59d43b","tid":717042,"uid":43839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"隻game 都無4K,材質又無4K<br />\n你用模擬器係出唔到4K野,你只係出到像素倍大左4畫面<br />\n唔通你玩GBA模擬器又叫玩4K咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nFurther testing may prove otherwise, but right now our contention is that The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild switches between two resolutions depending on configuration - so to confirm, that's 648p/720p on Wii U and Switch mobile, and 810p/900p on the docked Switch. <br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwii U  得720P,switch dock mode 900p<br />\n<br />\n720P 仲要倍上去4K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"2D同3D唔同<br />\n所有3D Model都係單純點同點連線、貼圖<br />\n無錯Texture係無4K, 但3D可以由Render 720p畫面變成Render做4K畫面<br />\n畫面一樣會清咗, 而且有Cemu有MOD可以改Level of Detail、View Distance<br />\n真係可以靚過Console玩<br />\n不過就真係少數PC先頂得順"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"主流1060 卡都可以啦<br />\n講畫面，一定係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}